MidPoint 4.8 "Curie" Update 12
-------------------------------

Release 4.8.12 is a seventy-seventh midPoint release code-named Curie.
The 4.8.12 release brings security, stability and miscellaneous bugfixes.

Release date: 1st June 2026
Release type: Long-term support release (LTS)
End of support: 17th October 2028

Please see the release notes for detailed list of changes:
https://docs.evolveum.com/midpoint/release/4.8.12/
